{{Infobox Character |name = Easel |image = Easel.png |species = [[Keves]]i human |age = 7th Term |gender = Female |haircolor = Red |eyecolor = Blue |affiliation = [[Syra Hovering Reefs]] ([[Colony 11]]) |voiceactorjp = |voiceactoreng = |appearances = {{XC3}} }} '''Easel''' is a character in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == Easel is a lieutenant of [[Colony 11]], and captain of the supply squad. [[Hexen]] and [[Branden]] are her subordinates. Additionally, she is one of the Three Ravens, along with her fellow lieutenants [[Zoren]] and [[Clad]]. As captain of the supply squad, she frequently goes on monster hunts and takes pride in being a hunter. As with the other lieutenants, she holds both respect and a grudge against [[Ashera]], and refers to her as her prey.
== Affinity == * [[Ashera]] * [[Clad]] * [[Zoren]] * [[Branden]] * [[Hexen]] {{clr}}
