{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Eghi Rhogul |image = Eghi Rhogul.png |caption = Eghi Rhogul |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Rhogul]] |level = 64 |area = [[Urayan Tunnels]] |spawntime = During and after ''[[Happiness]]'' |respawn = Yes |movement = |detection = Sight (Regardless of level difference) |exp = }} '''Eghi Rhoguls''' are [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Bosses]] in {{XC3}}. They are members of the [[Rhogul]] family, and can be found at level 64 at [[Urayan Tunnels]] in the [[Pentelas Region]] during ''[[Happiness]]''; however, it also respawns after the quest and are the only boss in the game to do so. During and after ''Happiness'', the four Eghi Rhoguls and one [[Rabdar Rhogul]] [[Elite Monster]] guard one [[Cozy Rhogul Egggems]] in their nest.
Despite being in the [[Great Cotte Falls]] area near the entrance to Urayan Tunnels, the map considers its location as part of Urayan Tunnels area. {{clr}}
